it ends...

541
01:10:14,920 --> 01:10:17,360
...as the song says.

542
01:10:17,720 --> 01:10:20,360
Marco, we need to talk afterwards.

543
01:10:20,640 --> 01:10:24,520
-We've been talking for an hour.
-You have, not me.

544
01:10:25,240 --> 01:10:27,200
You're right.

545
