My leg needs two months of therapy,
said the doctor.

546
01:10:56,160 --> 01:10:59,120
But you know what? I am glad
that bull hit me.

547
01:10:59,560 --> 01:11:02,800
Now I can stay with you until
you wake up.

548
01:11:02,800 --> 01:11:05,240
No one will take me away from you.

549
01:11:06,880 --> 01:11:10,120
We got back together,
a month ago...

550
01:11:11,440 --> 01:11:15,240
