wedding. She didn't in the end.

551
01:11:17,960 --> 01:11:20,680
It was you she cried for.

552
01:11:22,880 --> 01:11:27,240
She called me to tell me
she cried for me.

553
01:11:28,640 --> 01:11:31,400
Last time we spoke.

554
01:11:31,400 --> 01:11:34,760
