the visit.

686
01:22:43,800 --> 01:22:46,920
If he doesn't want to see you,
there is nothing we can do.

687
01:22:48,400 --> 01:22:52,360
And something else. We don't
have prisoners here...

688
01:22:53,360 --> 01:22:57,640
We don't have prisoners here,
we have lodgers.

689
01:23:33,080 --> 01:23:35,360
Marco, is that you?

690
01:23:36,240 --> 01:23:40,440
I am glad to hear your voice.
I asked your visit on Saturday.

691
01:23:42,800 --> 01:23:45,040
-Where are you?
-Outside the clinique.

692
01:23:47,120 --> 01:23:51,040
